            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ".)",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And the breadth thereof twenty cubits.—1Kings 6:20 adds that the height also was twenty cubits, so that the chamber formed a perfect cube.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "And the breadth thereof twenty cubits.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "1Kings 6:20",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " adds that the height also was twenty cubits, so that the chamber formed a perfect cube.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Six hundred talents.—The weight of gold thus expended on the plating of the walls of the inner shrine is not given in Kings. Solomon’s whole yearly revenue was 666 talents (1Kings 10:14).",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Six hundred talents.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—The weight of gold thus expended on the plating of the walls of the inner shrine is not given in Kings. Solomon’s whole yearly revenue was 666 talents (",
            "children": []
